# StackOverflow-Lite

StackOverflow-Lite is a question and answer application that provides users with the ability to ask questions and have their fellow users answer them.

## questions [/api/v1/questions/]

### Ask a quesion [POST]

You can ask a question sending the question_title and question_description.

+ Request (application/json)

            {
            "question_title": "What is Python?",
            "question_description": "Am a novice programmer and wanted to know what python language stands for"
            }
            
+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "response" : "You have successfully asked the question"
            }
            
+ Response 409 (application/json)

            {
                "response" : "question already exists"
            }
            
        

